&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Salaried GP&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Brandon Medical Practice&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; Salaried General Practitioner required at Brandon Medical Practice in Suffolk.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We believe in innovation, and delivering sustainable quality care to our patients. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;As part of Suffolk Primary care 13 like-minded practices at the forefront of change we share resources knowledge and skills to collaborate and build capability as well as capacity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; Through partnership we ensure best practice and the very best outcomes for our patients and communities. We are looking for a dedicated professional who will share our values and our passion for delivering quality care. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;You will be based at Brandon and will work alongside a multi-disciplinary team. You must have the following; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;• Full and current unrestricted GMC (UK) registration on the GP Register&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; • Excellent command of the English Language – both written and verbal &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;• Able to work under pressure and be a champion of change within an ever evolving environment &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;• Good interpersonal skills, and supportive as well as courteous to patients and colleagues alike&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; • Enthusiastic team player who is open and reflective and able to help others learn and develop.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;In return we will offer you;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;A highly competitive salary including NHS Pension, on-going training and development and good working conditions. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;There is genuine opportunity to innovate and specialise, and to play a key role in the continued development of the organisation. If our GP role appeals, you have the qualities we are looking for, share our values and feel excited by the prospect of what we can do for your career then we’d love to hear from you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Contact Kathryn Spencer &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;kathryn.spencer6@nhs.net&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;  or call 01842 810388 for an informal discussion and practice visit.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
